sets.title: Full throttle back & biceps
sets.summary: Pump your biceps and build your back for more lifting power.
sets.subTitle: Centr Power in Gym: Intermediate week 1

workouts.title: Workout
workouts.introText:
For biceps that pop and a strong back to dial up your lifting power, you've come to the right workout.


Don't compromise your form for heavier weights â€“ master good technique with the tutorial and control your tempo.

groups.title: Warm-up
groups.summary: Activate those lifting muscles with Bobby.

groups.title: Round 1
groups.summary: The wide grip puts the focus on your upper back.

groups.title: Round 2
groups.summary: Focus on your tempo to max time under tension for your muscles.

groups.title: Round 3
groups.summary: While your biceps are pumping, all the major muscles in your back are working hard with this move.

groups.title: Round 4
groups.summary: Use the underhand grip to target your lats, then switch to curls to isolate your biceps.
